Command.ВозвратКаретки.Title=\\r
Command.ВозвратКаретки.ToolTip=Matches a carriage return character (CR).
Command.ВпередиЕсть.Title=(?\=pattern)
Command.ВпередиЕсть.ToolTip=Positive lookahead. Matches the source string at any point where a match for pattern starts. This is a non-capturing match, meaning the matched value is not stored for possible later use.
Command.ВпередиНет.Title=(?\!pattern)
Command.ВпередиНет.ToolTip=Negative lookahead. Matches the source string at any point where there is no start of a match for pattern. This is a non-capturing match, meaning the matched value is not stored for possible later use.
