Command.ГраницаСлова.ToolTip=Matches a word boundary, i.e. the position between a word and a space.
Command.ДиапазонСимволов.Title=[a-z]
Command.ДиапазонСимволов.ToolTip=Character range. Matches any character within the specified range.
Command.ДиапазонСимволовОтриц.Title=[^a-z]
Command.ДиапазонСимволовОтриц.ToolTip=Negative character range. Matches any character outside the specified range.
