Command.НайтиИЗаменитьВсеВхожденияИмени.ToolTip=Find and replace all occurrences of the name
Command.НачалоСтроки.Title=^
Command.НачалоСтроки.ToolTip=Matches the position at the beginning of the input string. If the Multiline property of the RegExp object is set to True, ^ also matches the position after '\\n' or '\\r'.
Command.НеГраницаСлова.Title=\\B
Command.НеГраницаСлова.ToolTip=Matches all characters except a word boundary.
Command.НеИдентификатор.Title=\\W
Command.НеИдентификатор.ToolTip=Matches any character except a Latin letter, digit, or underscore. Equivalent to '[^A-Za-z0-9_]'.
Command.НеПробельныйСимвол.Title=\\S
Command.НеПробельныйСимвол.ToolTip=Matches any non-whitespace character. Equivalent to [^ \\f\\n\\r\\t\\v].
Command.НеЦифра.Title=\\D
Command.НеЦифра.ToolTip=Matches a non-digit character.
Command.ПереводСтроки.Title=\\n
Command.ПереводСтроки.ToolTip=Matches a line feed character (LF).
Command.Повтор01.Title=?
Command.Повтор01.ToolTip=Matches the preceding subexpression zero or one time.\nAfter any other quantifier (*, +, ?, {n}, {n,}, {n,m}), declares the pattern as "non-greedy"
Command.ПовторM.Title={,m}
Command.ПовторM.ToolTip=m and n are positive integers, with n <\= m. Matches at least n and at most m repetitions.
Command.ПовторN.Title={n}
Command.ПовторN.ToolTip=n is a positive integer. Matches exactly n repetitions.
Command.ПовторБольшеN.Title={n,}
Command.ПовторБольшеN.ToolTip=n is a positive integer. Matches at least n repetitions.
Command.ПовторОт0.Title=*
Command.ПовторОт0.ToolTip=Matches the preceding subexpression zero or more times.
